snippet.title: Pickle Wars gameplay (PC Game, 1994)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Pickle Wars, Dos PC game produced by MVP Software in 1994 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/pickle-wars/4650/
Pickle Wars is a platform game, full of action. The planet is invaded by aliens and you have somehow to help the general population.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
